Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:13.34,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:30.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:36.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:40.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:44.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:48.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:54.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:59.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:02.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:11.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(482.167,140.389)}The Shocker Leader Appears!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs195\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(417.167,710.389)}Rider in Peril
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These are the Alps, a mountain range\Nsometimes called the Roof of the World.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:34.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These mountains are home\Nto a Shocker secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is FBI Shocker investigator,\NAlps division, Pierre Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigator Taki, Japan division.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigator Taki, Japan division. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you read me, Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I read you loud and clear. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have acquired important\Ninformation on Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre, what's the information?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Radio transmission detected,\Nfifteen degrees right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from that mountain hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is sending their top secret\Nplans to Manazuru Beach in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming. Manazuru Beach,\Nat 10:00 tomorrow Japan time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you read me, Andre? Andre!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, Andre here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI scum...\Nyou've outlived your usefulness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre's been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We went through training together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let your information go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will strike down\NShocker and avenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting to the time Andre told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This stinks. I usually get huge\Nhauls at the worst times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I got another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Shocker plans\Non bringing in the secret plans here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Submarine? Transport plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right down to the second...\NThey're punctual, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complimenting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got your plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrieve the message capsule! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That way! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a haul of fish and Shocker's\Nmessage capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure, Tachibana Tobei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a cyborg based on the killer\Nof the sea, the saw shark... Girizames!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that message capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked hard to get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki has the Shocker message capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki does?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a powerful\Nmonster named Girizames...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost became fish bait myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker... this should slow you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a checkpoint, to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a Shocker checkpoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all members of Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:47.80,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:55.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:59.02,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:02.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:06.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:10.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:36.51,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:43.45,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:47.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:51.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:55.32,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... time to break through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived that, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The likes of you won't\Nkill the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Shocker planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You're Shocker's latest cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A cyborg based on the bandit\Nof the Pacific, the saw shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Girizames!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Girizames?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick Counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end of the Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Girizames...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kamen Rider! \NI haven't given up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:41.55,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Operation: V proceeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan is proceeding smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At last... at last, we'll bring\Nan end to that Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Taki and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,having acquired the message capsule,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,had asked FBI headquarters in\NNew York for help deciphering its code.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reply from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI's computers\Ncertainly are impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They deciphered that complicated\Ncode in just ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Read it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Shocker code deciphers as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,'The Shocker World Conference will\Nbe held on an island in Tokyo Bay
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,located at 35 degrees\N16 minutes north latitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Participating members will\Ninclude Shocker's leader
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and commanders from across the world.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Their leader's never\Nshown himself before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really putting in an appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. 35 degrees, 16 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who their leader is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My intuition tells me he's not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A cyborg, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No... he could well be an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The site of Shocker's world\Nconference is a former fortress island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Morocco Branch leader, Mohammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibraltar Branch leader, Humphrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore Branch leader, Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong Kong Branch leader, Chang Fou Ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:45.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Intruder in block C. Intruder in block C.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All men, go to yellow alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're after one thing\Nhere: Shocker's leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll lure out the\Ncombatants guarding the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Go avenge Andre for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I'm going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker World\NConference will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's theme is Operation: V.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Shocker leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to unmask him at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not about to reveal my face to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The radio message from the Alps,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the message capsule,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and the coded message inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all arranged to lure\Nyou here, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... so everything that\Nhappened was part of your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's great plan to\Nrid the world of Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the true nature of Operation: V.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then these men, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've taken\NShocker a bit too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think we'd\Nbring our commanders here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all mannequins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just any mannequins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mannequins designed to destroy Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Andro gas... made to destroy\Nthe body of a cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Girizames!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Girizames!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep Rider on the island\Nfor just five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The island is sinking into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The island is sinking? Taki's in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:19.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:23.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:27.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:34.35,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:37.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:44.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:48.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:52.34,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:02.97,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:06.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:10.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:13.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:17.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:20.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:26.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:31.67,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:35.75,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:46.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:53.43,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:57.02,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:00.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:04.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:07.03,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:10.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:15.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:18.84,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, did you find Shocker's leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A trap set to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The island is set to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Kamen Rider is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:23:01.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider had escaped\NShocker's terrible trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:04.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but the identity of Shocker's\Nleader remains a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.76,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:14.43,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(290.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:15.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:16.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Squidevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:19.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In a plot to kill Kamen\NRider once and for all,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:22.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami unleashes\Nthe mighty monster Squidevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But who is it, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:27.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The\NTerrifying Truth of Doctor Shinigami?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0.5\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,430.389)}The Terrifying Truth of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}Doctor Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:41.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:45.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.39,0:23:48.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:50.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:52.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:55.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:58.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:04.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:07.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:11.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:15.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(482.167,140.389)}The Shocker Leader Appears!!
Comment: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Terrifying Truth of Doctor Shinigami?
Comment: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}The Terrifying Truth of Doctor Shinigami?